Subject: [PATCH 2/4] feat(web): DPDP cookie consent banner

DPDP Act 2023 requires disclosure of cookie usage. Jovio only uses
essential cookies (Supabase session + CSRF token) so this is a
notice + acknowledge rather than a per-category toggle UI.

Banner appears bottom-of-screen on first visit. 'Got it' button
writes jovio-cookie-ack=1 to localStorage so it doesn't reappear.
Handles localStorage-blocked browsers gracefully (shows again on
next visit, no crash).

If we add analytics or advertising cookies later, this MUST be
replaced with a proper opt-in UI BEFORE setting those cookies.
